  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下Filecoin扇区的完整生命周期状态机，从Null开始，经过Precommitted、Committed，最终到Active或者被删除。你能帮我画一个状态图吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Null",
        "Precommitted",
        "Committed",
        "Active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解扇区从Null开始。PreCommitSectors是触发Precommitted状态的入口操作，对吗？还有，我看到有CronPreCommitExpiry这个超时机制，它会导致什么结果？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Null",
        "Precommitted",
        "PreCommitSectors",
        "CronPreCommitExpiry"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，PreCommitSectors让扇区进入Precommitted。如果超时没完成后续操作，CronPreCommitExpiry会触发，扇区直接变成Deleted状态，我们内部叫PCD（PreCommit Drop）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Precommitted",
        "Deleted",
        "CronPreCommitExpiry",
        "PCD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，Precommitted到Committed通过CommitSectors，然后Committed之后有两条主要路径：SubmittedWindowPoSt进入Active，或者出现各种故障情况。我先画出这条主线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Precommitted",
        "Committed",
        "CommitSectors",
        "SubmittedWindowPoSt",
        "Active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Committed状态其实挺复杂的。除了正常提交WindowPoSt变成Active，还可能因为DeclareFault、SubmitWindowPoSt失败或者ProvingDeadline触发而进入Faulty状态。这些情况都标记为SP（Skipped Proof）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Committed",
        "Faulty",
        "DeclareFault",
        "SubmitWindowPoSt",
        "ProvingDeadline",
        "SP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到Committed也能直接到Terminated，是通过TerminateSectors吗？这个TF标记是什么意思？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Committed",
        "Terminated",
        "TerminateSectors",
        "TF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，TF是Terminate Faulty的缩写，表示主动终止。矿工可以随时调用TerminateSectors把扇区终止掉，不管当前是什么状态，只要还没被删。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Terminated",
        "TerminateSectors",
        "TF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Faulty状态我画出来了。现在需要确认Faulty的转移：SubmittedWindowPoSt能回到Active，这个标记FF是Faulty Fixed的意思吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Faulty",
        "Active",
        "SubmittedWindowPoSt",
        "FF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确，FF就是Faulty Fixed。另外Faulty还有个自循环，ProvingDeadline（FF）表示持续处于故障状态，每次证明窗口都跳过。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Faulty",
        "ProvingDeadline",
        "FF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
